('370','1','0','Young $C, you shouldn\'t be wasting your time here in Brill when your people need you fighting for their cause. Now, take up arms and travel to the southwest, to the ruined tower, and slay Captain Perrine along with 3 Scarlet Zealots and 3 Scarlet Missionaries. We shall herd the Scarlet Crusade like cattle to their demise.'),
