('373','0','0','Yes? Is there something I can help you with?'),
('374','6','0','Have you collected 10 Scarlet Insignia Rings yet, $c?'),
('375','0','0','Do you have five Duskbat Pelts and some Coarse Thread yet, $N?'),
('376','0','0','Do try your best to keep yourself unharmed until I get you some armor.'),
('377','5','5','So long as a molester of the dead like Dextren Ward is permitted to live, justice stands betrayed. Return to me once Lord Ebonlocke\'s sentence of death is carried out on that defiler, Ward. We shall give the families of the dead the closure they deserve and better yet, we will send a clear message to the House of Nobles in Stormwind.'),
('378','1','1','I won\'t let foolish Human bureaucracy interfere with Dwarven matters, $N. Kam Deepfury is a proven conspirator in the Thandol Span attack. King Magni\'s good people lost their lives because of Deepfury\'s deceit. The Humans might be content to let Deepfury rot in The Stockade but I will not sleep soundly at night until Deepfury is slain.'),
('379','1','0','Well, did the nomads \'volunteer\' up those water pouches for you?'),
