('528','1','0','You have your orders, $c. Quit dawdling here in Tarren Mill when there is work to be done elsewhere.'),
('529','6','6','Were you able to carry out your orders, $C? Did you dispose of Verringtan and his assistants? And where is that iron shipment?'),
('530','6','6','Do you have those hands, $N?'),
('531','11','0','Great job, $N! We really showed him! Here, give me the head and I\'ll take care of it.'),
