('1249','1','0','Did he slip away? He looked a little shady the way he was watching us.'),
('1250','1','0',NULL),
('1251','6','0','What\'s that you have there, $n? Evidence from the remains of the Shady Rest Inn?'),
('1252','1','0','Have you found anything of interest at the Shady Rest Inn?'),
('1253','1','0','Have you found evidence from the site of the Shady Rest Inn?'),
('1258','1','0','My research with the Mudrock tongues is progressing nicely. I trust your crab hunt goes well?'),
('1259','1','0',NULL),
