('1366','0','0','How is your collection of ears, $N? Large?'),
('1367','1','0','Leave! The Magram do not speak with the weak. We kill them!$B$BIf you want to speak with me, then show me you are strong. Return after you slay many Gelkis.'),
('1368','1','0','Your two feet step on Gelkis earth. You are not welcome here!$B$BProve you seek friendship with the Gelkis. Kill Magram centaur. Return when the ground is wet with Magram blood.'),
('1369','1','0','If you are not our enemy, then you will do what I ask!'),
('1370','1','0','Return after you further prove your worth to the Gelkis!'),
('1371','1','0','If you are not our enemy, then you will do what I ask!'),
