('1486','0','0','I am very interested in examining the hides from the deviate creatures who have infested these caves. Have you had any luck in collecting some, $C?'),
('1487','1','0','$N, we, the Disciples of Naralex, need your help. Our numbers are dwindling with our master trapped in his twisted nightmare. We have not the forces necessary to deal with the corrupt creatures which now haunt these caverns.$b$bI beg of you, enter the caves and wage war on the deviate creatures!'),
('1488','1','15','Glory to the Horde, and death to our enemies, $N!$B$BThe demons in Desolace pose a greater threat than ever before. My hope of returning to the Warchief dwindles as more and more of the foul creatures seem to appear.$B$BI sometimes wish it was only the centaur we had to deal with.'),
