('2821','1','1','A stack of ten thick yeti hides will net you a choice of one of my crafted items.  Because I care about quality, I am able to ensure you\'ll get a good item!$B$BIf you can\'t seem to find yetis, I know where some might be.  Try looking just inland of the Forgotten Coast, around Feral Scar Vale.'),
