('5529','1','5','Get to the Scholomance, $N.  Take out those plagued hatchlings before they grow!'),
('5531','1','0','Hello, $N! I heard you were here with some dragon eggs? Well, let\'s see them!'),
('5533','1','0',''),
('5534','1','0','Well, $N? Where is the rune? You are a good employee, right? You\'re here to help?$b$bDon\'t make me think twice about paying you what we agreed upon. What? Oh, we didn\'t agree on anything? Oh, great... then take your time--just know that it\'ll be a lot less if you take a long time.'),
('5535','1','6','How goes your search for the Highborne spirits, $c?$B$BMany events have caused all the races of Azeroth great suffering, but for some reason, these spirits seem to be a plague for all people. Perhaps it is there continued desire for any arcane magic--such desire is a harbinger of the Burning Legion, and we know what that can lead to.'),
('5536','1','1','How goes your battle against the satyr, $c?$B$BAre they as strong as you thought? Stronger? Or perhaps they were nothing to your own might.'),
('5537','1','1','As morbid as it sounds, we\'ll need a decent supply of suitable skeletal fragments to make up the outer layer of the key.  They don\'t call it a Skeleton Key for nothing, you know.'),
('5538','1','0','Yeah, I know who you are, and I know why you\'re here. Dithers sent word to me before you arrived. Let\'s cut to deal at hand, now shall we?$b$bI\'ve got a mold you can use for the skeleton key, but it will cost you - fifteen gold, up front, no negotiation. I\'ll pack the skeletal fragments into the mold for you, and I\'ll also teach you on how to forge the stem of the key without any knowledge of blacksmithing... all free of charge no less.$b$bWho says mercenaries don\'t offer competitive deals!'),
('5541','6','6','I hope you\'re not here for ammo, because I\'m almost out!'),
('5542','1','5','Do not pity the demon dogs, $r. They are abominations!'),
('5543','1','1','Do not underestimate the winged vermin, $r. The Plague has given them supernatural abilities.'),
('5544','1','1','You will grow to tolerate the taste, $r.'),
