('6387','6','0','Have you had your fill of Thelsamar so soon? Are you ready to leave for another city?'),
('6388','6','0','You look like you have somewhere to go. Need one of my gryphons?'),
('6389','6','0','Have you done it, $N? Have you released the termites? The Light help us if the Scarlet Crusade were able to hold onto both the mill and Hearthglen. They should have neither. They\'re just capitalizing on the victims of the last war and should be put down like rabid animals!'),
('6390','6','6','Have you done it, $N? Have you released the termites in the lumber mill?$B$BIt was bad enough that my family lost their jobs and lives, but then to see the place where my childhood was spent taken over by those disgusting so-called holy men... pfah!!'),
