('6392','6','0','Ah, $N. Have you returned from Ironforge?'),
('6393','1','0','The Tribunal of the Tides grows impatient. They seek to end this war that has raged across all dimensions for eons. My brethren are anxious to hear news of the glorious victory over the hated fire elementals. Have you the Incendrites that I require?'),
('6394','0','0','Have you entered the Burning Blade Coven, $N? Did you find my pick?'),
('6395','1','1','We must respect our dead, $N. It is one of the ways in which we differ from the Scourge...'),
