('6801','1','0','I come from Thunder Bluff, $r. Cairne himself has seen to it that I assist the Frostwolf Clan in these dire times.$b$bBut let us not waste any more time. You must strike down our enemies and bring to me their blood. Once enough blood has been gathered, the ritual of summoning may begin.$b$bVictory will be assured when the elemental lord is loosed upon the Stormpike army.'),
