('6881','1','0','The Frostwolf Clan is protected by a taint of elemental energy. Their shaman meddle in powers that will surely destroy us all if left unchecked.$b$bThe damage has grown too great for the Circle to control! Ivus must be called to our aid.$b$bThe Frostwolf soldiers carry elemental charms called storm crystals. We can use the charms to conjure Ivus. Venture forth and claim the crystals, $n!'),
